title: #92Noon: Aftermath Monday
description: Montage, takes, talkers and calls following the Vikings 27-10 playoff loss in SanFrancisco...hear a Mike Zimmer season-ending press conference in the final hour...Plus, Dave Sinykin joins for a border battle segment since the Packers are in the NFC title game.
